 the center console, the center armrest, and door armrests all sport the same red and copper double stitching.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eEven the floormats feature RS 6 GT lettering as does the center-console badge that displays your particular example\u0026#39;s number out of 660.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2025 Audi RS 6 Avant GT\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDEzMTk5/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg\" height=\"3721\" width=\"4961\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e2025 Audi RS 6 Avant GT\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAudi\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"even-the-rs-6-avant-gt-s-factory-is-special\"\u003eEven the RS 6 Avant GT\u0026#39;s factory is special\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnlike the regular RS 6 Avant, the special edition GT leaves the Neckarsulm production line after body construction works and paint. Each unit heads to Böllinger Höfe, where models such as the Audi R8 and the RS e-tron GT are built.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFinal assembly is carried out by seven experienced craftspeople at three assembly stations set up especially for this exclusive special edition, spending an entire day on site. All GT-specific features are fitted by hand, including the hood, fenders, rocker panels, double wing, the front and rear aprons, and the adjustable coilover suspension.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/2026-audi-a6-avant-debuts-to-fight-bmw-5-series-touring\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2025 Audi RS 6 Avant GT\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg\" height=\"3721\" width=\"4961\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e\u003cem\u003e2025 Audi RS 6 Avant GT\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAudi\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eOf course, such a tremendous automobile is a limited affair, with only 85 units produced in the U.S. and 660 globally. The Audi RS 6 Avant GT was released in late 2024 with an MSRP of $198,900, but good luck finding one on the second-hand market.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGiven its limited release, used examples will undoubtedly command a premium when they do hit sites like Bring a Trailer or Cars \u0026amp; Bids. Do you think a tribute like this is worth the near $200,000 price tag, or would it need to have a lot more added features for that kind of dough?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv phx-gallery=\"\"\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-full-height=\"1500\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNTQ0Mjcx/original-13483-a237132-large.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f5f917c00025cf\" data-image-slug=\"Original-13483-a237132-large\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNTQ0Mjcx\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-full-height=\"1500\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDc4NzM1/original-13482-a237129-large.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f5f917c000275d\" data-image-slug=\"Original-13482-a237129-large\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNDc4NzM1\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-full-height=\"1500\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNjA5ODA3/original-13490-a237093-large.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f5f917d00125cf\" data-image-slug=\"Original-13490-a237093-large\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMzUwNDM1NjIzNjA5ODA3\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-full-height=\"1500\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzgzNTE3/original-13492-a237106-large.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"ci02f5f917e00025cf\" data-image-slug=\"Original-13492-a237106-large\" data-public-id=\"MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzgzNTE3\"\u003e\u003c/phx-gallery-image\u003e\u003cphx-gallery-image data-full-height=\"1500\" data-full-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Ch_2000%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_2000/MjEzMzUwNDM1ODkxNzE3OTgx/2025-audi-rs-6-avant-gt.jpg\" data-full-width=\"2000\" data-image-id=\"